*--- LNOBJ test ---
*
* Tests #LNOBJ: WAV ZZ acts as LN end marker.
* Lane 1 (ch11): normal note at beat 0, LNOBJ at beat 2 → LN from beat 0 to beat 2
* Lane 2 (ch12): normal note at beat 0, LNOBJ at beat 3 → LN from beat 0 to beat 3
* Lane 3 (ch13): two normal notes (no LNOBJ match) → remain normal

